name: ASA THE BUNNY GIRL
description:
FRIDAY. 09:15 AM. 

The new girl at Miku's college seems kind of strange.

People have heard her making scary, guttural sounds alone in the bathroom cubicles...

She always has a smell of raw, rotten meat lingering around her...

And nobody knows exactly where she came from.

Miku kind of feels sorry for her.

Maybe she could just use a friend?
